<section class="win-section" id="buttons">
    <header class="win-section-header row">
        <h1 class="win-section-title col-xs-24">
            <a href="#buttons">Buttons</a>
        </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-24">
            <p>The colors used for the background and text of buttons have been vetted to meet a minimum color contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for accesibility purposes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p><strong>Using <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> tag.</strong> The <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> tag should be used for links between pages, not for JavaScript actions.</p>
            <p>Rest state</p>
            <p>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-default">Default</a>                
                <a href="" class="btn btn-primary">Primary</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-success">Success</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-info">Info</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-warning">Warning</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-danger">Danger</a>
            </p>
            <p>Disabled state</p>
            <p>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-default disabled">Default disabled</a>                
                <a href="" class="btn btn-primary disabled">Primary disabled</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-success disabled">Success disabled</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-info disabled">Info disabled</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-warning disabled">Warning disabled</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-danger disabled">Danger disabled</a>
            </p>
            <p>Active (on click/mouse down) state</p>
            <p>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-default active">Default active</a>                
                <a href="" class="btn btn-primary active">Primary active</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-success active">Success active</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-info active">Info active</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-warning active">Warning active</a>
                <a href="" class="btn btn-danger active">Danger active</a>   
            </p>

            {{#markdown}}
```xml
<a href="" class="btn [btn-default] [btn-primary] [btn-success] [btn-info] [btn-warning] [btn-danger] [disabled] [active]">
    Button link
</a>
```
            {{/markdown}}
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p><strong>Using <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> tag.</strong> The <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> tag is used on forms and for JavaScript actions.</p>           
            <p>Rest state</p>
            <p>
                <button class="btn btn-default">Default</button>                
                <button class="btn btn-primary">Primary</button>
                <button class="btn btn-success">Success</button>                
                <button class="btn btn-info">Info</button>
                <button class="btn btn-warning">Warning</button>
                <button class="btn btn-danger">Danger</button>
                <button class="btn btn-link">Link</button>
            </p>
            <p>Disabled state</p>
            <p>
                <button class="btn btn-default" disabled>Default disabled</button>                
                <button class="btn btn-primary" disabled>Primary disabled</button>
                <button class="btn btn-success" disabled>Success disabled</button>                
                <button class="btn btn-info" disabled>Info disabled</button>
                <button class="btn btn-warning" disabled>Warning disabled</button>
                <button class="btn btn-danger" disabled>Danger disabled</button>
                <button class="btn btn-link" disabled>Link disabled</button>
            </p>
            <p>Active (on click/mouse down) state</p>
            <p>
                <button class="btn btn-default active">Default active</button>               
                <button class="btn btn-primary active">Primary active</button>
                <button class="btn btn-success active">Success active</button>                
                <button class="btn btn-info active">Info active</button>
                <button class="btn btn-warning active">Warning active</button>
                <button class="btn btn-danger active">Danger active</button>
                <button class="btn btn-link active">Link active</button>
            </p>

            {{#markdown}}
```xml
<button type="button"
       [disabled]
        class="btn [btn-default] [btn-primary] [btn-success] [btn-info] [btn-warning] [btn-danger] [active]">
    Button
</button>
```
            {{/markdown}}
        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-24">
            <h2>Buttons sizes</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p>
                Button sizes from extra small, small, normal to large.
            </p>
            <p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-xs">Extra small button</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Small button</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Normal button</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Large button</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary win-btn-xl">Extra large button</button>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p>
                A full width button that can be used with the various sizes.
            </p>
            <p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-xs">Extra small block button</button>
            </p>
            <p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-sm">Small block button</button>
            </p>
            <p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Normal block button</button>
            </p>
            <p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg">Large block button</button>
            </p>
            <p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block win-btn-xl">Extra large block button</button>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-24">
            <h2>Button groups (aka Choice buttons)</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p>
                <button type="button" class="btn win-btn-choice btn-lg btn-block" data-toggle="button" aria-pressed="false">
                    Choice
                </button>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p>
                <button type="button" class="btn win-btn-choice btn-lg btn-block" data-toggle="button" aria-pressed="false">
                    Another choice
                </button>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-24">
            {{#markdown}}
```xml
<button type="button" class="btn win-btn-choice btn-lg btn-block"
       [data-toggle="button"]
        aria-pressed="false|true">
    Choice
</button>
```
            {{/markdown}}
        </div>

